    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty in person! It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and ready for its next adventure, this is the one! Let's get you behind the wheel today! \u2728",
