    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the naturally aspirated S54B32 inline-six with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS. This specimen is mechanically flawless, featuring documented subframe reinforcement, a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing, and preventative rod bearing replacement. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate entry, transmitting power through a factory M Variable Differential Lock. Finished in concours-level condition with zero deferred maintenance, the chassis remains rigid and the suspension bushings are refreshed to OEM specifications. This is a turnkey performance icon for the discerning collector.",
