    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of pristine leather and untouched surfaces, still retaining that signature new-car aroma. Every feature, from the premium audio system to the advanced driver assists, functions with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, maintained with an open checkbook and backed by a comprehensive service history. The engine bay is immaculate, and the ride is as tight and responsive as a factory-fresh model. For the discerning buyer who refuses to compromise on quality, this is the definitive example of the marque.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
