    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting an impeccable exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory luster. Meticulously serviced and stored in a climate-controlled environment, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising quality. Every component functions with precision, reflecting a history of rigorous care and minimal use. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate the superior provenance of this investment-grade automobile.",
